OL,3,CHillary Clinton denies knowing Epstein
OL,4,Cand calls for Trump to be questioned
OL,6,FThe hearing, which is being held
OL,7,Fbehind closed doors, was stopped after
OL,8,Fa photo of Hillary Clinton giving
OL,9,Fevidence was posted online, as ITV
OL,10,FNews US Correspondent Dan Rivers
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FFormer Secretary of State Hillary
OL,14,FClinton has said she has no knowledge
OL,15,Fof Jeffrey Epstein's or Ghislaine
OL,16,FMaxwell's crimes while testifying as
OL,17,Fpart of a congressional investigation
OL,18,Finto the convicted sex offender.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
