OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772216417
OL,3,CHillary Clinton denies knowing Epstein
OL,4,Cand calls for Trump to be questioned
OL,6,F"I had no idea about their criminal
OL,7,Factivities. I do not recall ever
OL,8,Fencountering Mr Epstein," Hillary
OL,9,FClinton said in an opening statement
OL,10,Fshe shared on social media.
OL,12,FShe also urged politicians to ask US
OL,13,FPresident Donald Trump about Epstein
OL,14,Fwhile under oath.
