OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772216417
OL,3,CHillary Clinton denies knowing Epstein
OL,4,Cand calls for Trump to be questioned
OL,6,F"If this Committee is serious about
OL,7,Flearning the truth about Epstein's
OL,8,Ftrafficking crimes, it would not rely
OL,9,Fon press gaggles to get answers from
OL,10,Four current president on his
OL,11,Finvolvement; it would ask him directly
OL,12,Funder oath about the tens of thousands
OL,13,Fof times he shows up in the Epstein
OL,14,Ffiles," she wrote.
OL,16,FThe deposition was paused after
OL,17,FRepublican representative Lauren
OL,18,FBoebert sent a photo of the closed-
OL,19,Fdoor proceeding to a conservative
OL,20,Finfluencer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
