OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772216417
OL,3,CHillary Clinton denies knowing Epstein
OL,4,Cand calls for Trump to be questioned
OL,6,FBenny Johnson, a right-wing YouTuber,
OL,7,Fposted a photo of Clinton at the
OL,8,Fdeposition and said Boebert had
OL,9,Fprovided it.
OL,11,FThe deposition is being recorded on
OL,12,Fvideo, but Comer has said that it will
OL,13,Fonly be released after Clinton's
OL,14,Fattorneys have a chance to review it.
OL,15,FThe committee's rules do not allow
OL,16,Foutside press or photographers to take
OL,17,Fphotos of the proceedings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
