OL,3,CHillary Clinton denies knowing Epstein
OL,4,Cand calls for Trump to be questioned
OL,6,FThe depositions come after months of
OL,7,Ftense back-and-forth between Clinton,
OL,8,Fher husband and former US President
OL,9,FBill Clinton, and the Republican-
OL,10,Fcontrolled House Oversight Committee.
OL,12,FBill Clinton is also scheduled to
OL,13,Fappear in front of lawmakers. It will
OL,14,Fbe the first time a former president
OL,15,Fhas been forced to testify before
OL,16,FCongress.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
