OL,3,CHillary Clinton denies knowing Epstein
OL,4,Cand calls for Trump to be questioned
OL,6,FTrump has expressed regret over the
OL,7,FClintons being forced to testify. The
OL,8,Fpair agreed to testify last year after
OL,9,Ftheir offers of sworn statements were
OL,10,Frebuffed by the Oversight panel.
OL,12,F"We have a very clear record that
OL,13,Fwe've been willing to talk about,"
OL,14,FHillary Clinton said in an interview
OL,15,Fwith the BBC earlier this month.
