OL,3,CHillary Clinton denies knowing Epstein
OL,4,Cand calls for Trump to be questioned
OL,6,FShe added that her husband had flown
OL,7,Fwith Epstein for charitable trips and
OL,8,Fthat she did not recall meeting
OL,9,FEpstein but had interacted with
OL,10,FGhislaine Maxwell, Epstein's former
OL,11,Fgirlfriend and confidant, at
OL,12,Fconferences hosted by the Clinton
OL,13,FFoundation.
OL,15,F"We are more than happy to say what we
OL,16,Fknow, which is very limited and
OL,17,Ftotally unrelated to their behaviour
OL,18,For their crimes, and we want to do it
OL,19,Fin public," Hillary Clinton said.
