OL,3,CHillary Clinton denies knowing Epstein
OL,4,Cand calls for Trump to be questioned
OL,6,FSeveral photos of the former president
OL,7,Fwere included in the first tranche of
OL,8,FEpstein files released by the
OL,9,FDepartment of Justice in January,
OL,10,Fincluding a number of him with women
OL,11,Fwhose faces were redacted. Clinton has
OL,12,Fnot been accused of wrongdoing in his
OL,13,Frelationship with Epstein.
OL,15,FThe Oversight panel's chairman,
OL,16,FRepresentative James Comer, has
OL,17,Fpointed to Hillary Clinton's work as
OL,18,Fsecretary of state to address sex
OL,19,Ftrafficking as another reason to
OL,20,Finsist on her deposition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
