OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1772216417
OL,3,CHillary Clinton denies knowing Epstein
OL,4,Cand calls for Trump to be questioned
OL,6,FThe committee's investigation has
OL,7,Fsought to understand why the
OL,8,FDepartment of Justice under previous
OL,9,Fpresidential administrations did not
OL,10,Fseek further charges against Epstein
OL,11,Ffollowing a 2008 arrangement in which
OL,12,Fhe pleaded guilty to state charges in
OL,13,FFlorida for soliciting prostitution
OL,14,Ffrom an underage girl but avoided
OL,15,Ffederal charges.
OL,17,FThere is no suggestion that appearing
OL,18,Fin the Epstein documents, millions of
OL,19,Ffiles relating to the late sex
OL,20,Foffender, implies any wrongdoing
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
